            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Gen</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> ||(centurionum) p<expan><ex>rae</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ositorum</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Macal</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Avitus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Vital</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Respectus <lb n="4"/>cives Suebi Nicr<lb break="no" n="5"/>e<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>se</abbr></expan><surplus>n</surplus>s his qui or<lb break="no" n="6"/>dines sequentur <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ono</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ederunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Leseabweichungen. (C): Datierung: Ende 2./Anfang 3. Jh. Z. 1: Cüppers: Genio (centuriarum) p(rimi)p(ilorum); Schillinger-Häfele: Genio (centuriarum) pp(eregrinorum). (centuriarum) pp(eregrinorum).</p>
            </div>
